        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This staff is tapered at the base and carved into a gem-studded twist at the top. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify elemental creatures.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Frostbite]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Breathe Fire], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Pummeling Rubble], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Thunderstrike]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Blazing Bolt], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Resist Energy]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fireball], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Lightning Bolt]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Resist Energy], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Fire]</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Howling Blizzard], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wall of Ice]</em></li>\n<li><strong>6th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Chain Lightning]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fireball]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed ranks of all listed spells.</p>"
